column5: Had a beautiful afternoon for some family time. Lots of fish to catch. Judy outfished us all.    She won't bait the hook, and she won't touch the fish, but she still had a lot of fun.
Right on, looks like a good time was had! What is that first fish she caught??
Looks like some kind of chub .
Looks like a great day and she schooled you all
Dang !!!...I haven't had a feed of mudcats in many, many moons...Looks good Bruce...
Judy caught a few mooneye  Looks like a golden shinner!
